OL,3,CFirst Minister to work with No 10 but
OL,4,Cstresses need to 'respect Welsh
OL,5,Cdemocracy'
OL,7,FFirst Minister Rhun ap Iorwerth has
OL,8,Fvowed to "work closely" with the UK
OL,9,FGovernment while stressing "the need
OL,10,Fto respect Welsh democracy" following
OL,11,Fhis first call with the Welsh
OL,12,FSecretary.
OL,14,FThe First Minister said he spoke to
OL,15,FSecretary of State for Wales Jo
OL,16,FStevens on Monday morning (18 May),
OL,17,Fwhich follows Plaid Cymru's Senedd
OL,18,Felection victory earlier this month.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
