PN,46202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779127867
OL,3,CFirst Minister to work with No 10 but
OL,4,Cstresses need to 'respect Welsh
OL,5,Cdemocracy'
OL,7,FMr ap Iorwerth stated cost of living
OL,8,Fas an example of an issue that the UK
OL,9,FGovenrment and Welsh Government would
OL,10,F"work closely" on, while emphasising
OL,11,Fthe need to "respect Welsh democracy."
OL,13,FAccording to the First Minister's
OL,14,FOffice, other "shared interests" that
OL,15,Fwere discussed included steelmaking,
OL,16,Fcross-border collaboration, security
OL,17,Fand defence, and infrastructure and
OL,18,Fenergy.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
