FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779127867
OL,3,CFirst Minister to work with No 10 but
OL,4,Cstresses need to 'respect Welsh
OL,5,Cdemocracy'
OL,7,FThe Welsh Secretary said she
OL,8,Fcongratulated the First Minister on
OL,9,Fhis party's campaign and election
OL,10,Fresults and looked forward to "working
OL,11,Fconstructively" together on shared
OL,12,Fissues and priorities.
OL,14,FA readout of the phone call from the
OL,15,FFirst Minister's Office said: "As
OL,16,Fraised with the Prime Minister, he
OL,17,F(the First Minister) would like Welsh
OL,18,FGovernment Cabinet Ministers to engage
OL,19,Fdirectly with UKG counterparts, while
OL,20,Frecognising a continuing conduit role
OL,21,Ffor the Wales Office."
OL,26,@yD@ApmyD@Tpn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
