CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779127867
OL,3,CFirst Minister to work with No 10 but
OL,4,Cstresses need to 'respect Welsh
OL,5,Cdemocracy'
OL,7,FMeanwhile, the Wales Office said the
OL,8,Fcall "made clear the benefit of both
OL,9,Fthe UK and Welsh Governments working
OL,10,Ftogether", and emphasised that
OL,11,Fincluded the delivery of "clean energy
OL,12,Finfrastructure" in Wales, alongside
OL,13,Fthe other shared priorities.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
