OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779127867
OL,3,CFirst Minister to work with No 10 but
OL,4,Cstresses need to 'respect Welsh
OL,5,Cdemocracy'
OL,7,FThe conversation comes after the First
OL,8,FMinister's phone call with Prime
OL,9,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer last week,
OL,10,Fwho had proposed a face-to-face
OL,11,Fmeeting with the leaders of the
OL,12,Fdevolved governments in June after
OL,13,Fconfirming he would be "open to a
OL,14,Fconversation" about devolving more
OL,15,Fpowers from Westminster.
OL,26,@uD@XOUvD@MO]
