PN,46206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779127867
OL,3,CFirst Minister to work with No 10 but
OL,4,Cstresses need to 'respect Welsh
OL,5,Cdemocracy'
OL,7,FFirst Minister Rhun ap Iorwerth also
OL,8,Fopened his first Cabinet meeting
OL,9,Ftoday, calling it a "historic moment"
OL,10,Ffor Wales and a "privilege" to begin
OL,11,Fthe work of "doing our best for our
OL,12,Fcommunities and our nation."
OL,14,FHe said: "I know from the
OL,15,Fconversations we had last week how
OL,16,Fmuch being sat around this table means
OL,17,Fto you, so I'd like to place on record
OL,18,Fhow much it means to me too to be on
OL,19,Fthis journey with such talented and
OL,20,Fdedicated colleagues.
OL,26,@vD@JOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779127867
OL,3,CFirst Minister to work with No 10 but
OL,4,Cstresses need to 'respect Welsh
OL,5,Cdemocracy'
OL,7,F"It is my privilege to lead a team
OL,8,Fthat I know will work hard every day
OL,9,Fto improve the lives of the people of
OL,10,FWales...
OL,12,FHe went on to say: "We have an
OL,13,Fambitious but credible programme, and
OL,14,Fan excellent team of civil servants
OL,15,Fled by the Permanent Secretary, and I
OL,16,Fam confident that we will be able to
OL,17,Fachieve a lot together.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@TOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779127867
OL,3,CFirst Minister to work with No 10 but
OL,4,Cstresses need to 'respect Welsh
OL,5,Cdemocracy'
OL,7,F"I want the next four years to be
OL,8,Fdefined by four principles -
OL,9,Fprofessionalism, ambition, credibility
OL,10,Fand empathy. I ask each of you to keep
OL,11,Fthose in mind in your work every day
OL,12,Fand I promise to do the same.
OL,14,F"The challenges are great and the time
OL,15,Fis short but I am already encouraged
OL,16,Fby the way we have moved so quickly to
OL,17,Fturn our vision into reality and to
OL,18,Funderline all the ways this
OL,19,Fadministration represents new energy,
OL,20,Fnew ideas and new leadership," Mr ap
OL,21,FIorwerth added.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU|D@^O]
